{"article_id":"Ay1IkZAjKdwpScYk","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Bernie Sanders says","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"Hillary Clinton will not have sewn up the nomination on June 7 .","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"|","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"Getty","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"Bernie 's California endgame","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"If Sanders wins the biggest and most delegate-rich primary ,","depth":3},{"id":6,"text":"all bets are off .","depth":3},{"id":7,"text":"LOS ANGELES -","depth":3},{"id":8,"text":"Barring a set of unprecedented upsets on Tuesday ,","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"Hillary Clinton is expected to be declared the presumptive Democratic nominee .","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"And","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"when the television networks make that call","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"as soon as New Jersey polls close on June 7 ,","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"it will leave Bernie Sanders with a hard choice :","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"whether to directly acknowledge it","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"or intensify his fight to the July convention in Philadelphia .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"The Vermont senator has shown few signs","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"of being ready to concede .","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"And","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"if he wins California ,","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"he wo n't .","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"The outcome there will determine the course","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"he takes in the seven-week runup to the convention ,","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"top Sanders aides and high-profile supporters say ,","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"either driving his decision to battle on for the nomination","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"or to begin focusing on the party policy and platform changes","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"he wants to make .","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"A win in California ,","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"his top advisers believe ,","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"will enable Sanders to make a much more aggressive pitch to superdelegates and Democrats around the country in the coming weeks .","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"He will be able to point to victories over Clinton in more than 20 states","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"- capped by the biggest , bluest and most diverse in the nation .","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"The symbolic value","depth":13},{"id":33,"text":"of winning California ,","depth":13},{"id":34,"text":"they think ,","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"would underscore his point","depth":13},{"id":36,"text":"that the future of the party is on his side","depth":13},{"id":37,"text":"and rattle superdelegate confidence in her candidacy .","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"A loss , however , would dismantle that argument .","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"The Sanders camp believes","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"a defeat there would take the wind out of his sails ,","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"in no small part because of the negative media narrative","depth":15},{"id":42,"text":"that would result","depth":15},{"id":43,"text":"after having spent so much time in the state .","depth":14},{"id":44,"text":"Sanders hasn ' t directly addressed the issue","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"of how he ' ll respond Tuesday evening ,","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"though it ' s clearly something","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"that ' s on his mind .","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"He has shown no outward sign","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"of bowing to the increasingly loud grumblings from Clinton-allied officials","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"- most recently Senate Minority Leader Harry Reid -","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"urging him to drop out after California ,","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"and he brushes aside the suggestion","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"that his prolonged primary challenge could hurt Clinton against Donald Trump .","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"\" On Tuesday night , on the 7th , you ' re going to hear from the media saying","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"that Hillary Clinton has received whatever it is","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"- 80 or 90 delegates -","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"which she certainly will from New Jersey and other states ,","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"and they ' ll say","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"the primary process is over ,","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"Secretary Clinton has won , \"","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"Sanders told a crowd in Santa Cruz last week .","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"\" The Democratic National Committee will tell you","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"it ' s not factually correct .","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"The truth is no candidate","depth":14},{"id":65,"text":"- not Hillary Clinton , not Bernie Sanders -","depth":14},{"id":66,"text":"will receive the number of pledged delegates ,","depth":14},{"id":67,"text":"that is , the real delegates","depth":15},{"id":68,"text":"that people vote for .","depth":15},{"id":69,"text":"Neither candidate will have received the number of pledged delegates","depth":13},{"id":70,"text":"that he or she needs","depth":14},{"id":71,"text":"to become the Democratic nominee .","depth":14},{"id":72,"text":"What that means is that the superdelegates will be the people","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"who determine","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"who the nominee is . \"","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"\" The media is in error","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"when they lumped superdelegates with pledged delegates .","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"Pledged delegates are real , \"","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"he reiterated in a combative news conference in Los Angeles on Saturday .","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"\" The Democratic National Convention will be a contested convention . \"","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"Sanders has promised to give every voter a chance","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"to weigh in ,","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"meaning he will compete in Washington , D.C. ' s June 14 primary","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"-","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"for which his campaign has recently sought volunteer housing .","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"But even within Sanders circles , there is considerable head-scratching and puzzling through back-of-the-envelope delegate math","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"in an attempt","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"to figure out what the senator will do next .","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"Some aides near the top rungs of his political operation report","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"being told to focus exclusively on Tuesday ' s primaries ,","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"and not to worry about what comes next .","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"\" Basically , he decides daily .","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"What decides what happens after Tuesday is going to depend on what the results are , \"","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"said Dottie Deans , chairwoman of the Vermont Democratic Party and a superdelegate","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"who supports Sanders .","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"\" They ' ll sit down Wednesday","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"and they ' ll discuss what happened on Tuesday","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"and decide how to go forward . ''","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"\" I will accept any decision","depth":13},{"id":99,"text":"he makes ,","depth":13},{"id":100,"text":"and I will respect any decision","depth":13},{"id":101,"text":"he makes , \"","depth":13},{"id":102,"text":"she added .","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"\" But I ' m not in any position","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"to tell him what to do .","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"Nor would he listen to me . \"","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"One consensus expectation is that the Sanders campaign team will seek to leverage the senator ' s all-but-ensured status as the most successful runner-up in modern Democratic politics .","depth":6},{"id":107,"text":"Supporters listen to Bernie Sanders during a campaign rally at Qualcomm Stadium on June 5 in San Diego .","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"|","depth":7},{"id":109,"text":"AP Photo","depth":6},{"id":110,"text":"The possibilities include pledging to fight on with meetings and rallies ,","depth":6},{"id":111,"text":"all the while making the case to superdelegates","depth":7},{"id":112,"text":"that polls show","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"he is the stronger nominee against Donald Trump in November .","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"Or he could effectively concede the nomination","depth":6},{"id":115,"text":"and prepare his troops for platform fights and a contentious convention in Philadelphia .","depth":6},{"id":116,"text":"Sanders has a wide array of options","depth":8},{"id":117,"text":"as he pursues his stated goal","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"of persuading super delegates","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"- whose very existence he decries -","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"to switch their support from Clinton to him .","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"He could , for example , hold swing state rallies","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"to make the case against nominating Clinton , an approach","depth":13},{"id":123,"text":"that might let him maintain the earned media","depth":14},{"id":124,"text":"that sustains his public image .","depth":14},{"id":125,"text":"But that tack is unlikely .","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"He hasn ' t unleashed a new argument against Clinton in weeks ,","depth":14},{"id":127,"text":"indicating a diminished appetite for that kind of combat ,","depth":14},{"id":128,"text":"and a purple-state assault could weaken her against Trump .","depth":13},{"id":129,"text":"In addition , people close to the campaign expect the operation to severely cut back on travel","depth":11},{"id":130,"text":"after he ' s spent over two weeks straight in California ,","depth":12},{"id":131,"text":"largely because of the expense .","depth":12},{"id":132,"text":"The campaign has already been drastically slashing costs ,","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"and the staff is now down nearly to the group of senior advisers and an advance staff","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"that ' s necessary for large events .","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"A lower-profile , but cheaper avenue","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"to pursue","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"might be to meet individually with as many super delegates as possible in an effort","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"to swing them .","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"But more and more of these party leaders and officials have spoken up about how difficult that would be","depth":13},{"id":140,"text":"after he ' s denounced the superdelegate system in the first place ,","depth":13},{"id":141,"text":"and prominent Sanders backers say","depth":13},{"id":142,"text":"they don ' t view this alone as a practical option .","depth":13},{"id":143,"text":"It would likely take something more drastic to win over the superdelegates :","depth":12},{"id":144,"text":"none of those","depth":14},{"id":145,"text":"who support Clinton","depth":14},{"id":146,"text":"have been persuaded to swing to Sanders ' side in the year-plus of campaigning so far .","depth":13},{"id":147,"text":"One option","depth":14},{"id":148,"text":"floated by some Democrats","depth":15},{"id":149,"text":"- but not a popular one among Sanders ' most ardent backers -","depth":15},{"id":150,"text":"is that he could concede","depth":15},{"id":151,"text":"that Clinton is the nominee","depth":15},{"id":152,"text":"but encourage his army of delegates to fight for specific platform points and rules changes at the July convention .","depth":14},{"id":153,"text":"This might be the most realistic conciliatory route ,","depth":14},{"id":154,"text":"said some party officials","depth":15},{"id":155,"text":"thinking through the options ,","depth":15},{"id":156,"text":"noting","depth":14},{"id":157,"text":"that it ' s similar to the approach","depth":16},{"id":158,"text":"taken by Ted Cruz ,","depth":16},{"id":159,"text":"who maintained until the final days of his campaign","depth":16},{"id":160,"text":"that he ' d fight on to the GOP convention .","depth":16},{"id":161,"text":"But the Vermont senator has repeatedly insisted","depth":13},{"id":162,"text":"that he will take his leverage to Philadelphia ,","depth":13},{"id":163,"text":"and his senior advisers have not seriously thought through how that would look","depth":13},{"id":164,"text":"without him as an active candidate .","depth":13},{"id":165,"text":"Not expecting a concession of any sort ,","depth":8},{"id":166,"text":"Sanders ' allies universally expect","depth":9},{"id":167,"text":"a major part of his role in the coming weeks will be to outline his convention hopes to his delegates .","depth":9},{"id":168,"text":"\" I think","depth":10},{"id":169,"text":"what he ' s going to do is provide a lot of direction","depth":11},{"id":170,"text":"about what happens at the [ convention ] ,","depth":11},{"id":171,"text":"assuming the [ Democratic National Committee ] is not going to embrace our agenda .","depth":10},{"id":172,"text":"But we are going to be in a position","depth":11},{"id":173,"text":"to at least have a minority report and vote","depth":12},{"id":174,"text":"to put our issues on the agenda , \"","depth":12},{"id":175,"text":"said RoseAnn DeMoro , the executive director of the Sanders-backing National Nurses United union ,","depth":10},{"id":176,"text":"who referred to Tuesday ' s expected declaration of Clinton as the nominee as a \" big lie . \"","depth":10},{"id":177,"text":"\" The pivot , I don ' t know .","depth":10},{"id":178,"text":"It depends on how corrupt the DNC actually is","depth":13},{"id":179,"text":"once we get to Philadelphia , \"","depth":13},{"id":180,"text":"she said .","depth":12},{"id":181,"text":"\" That could determine the direction","depth":12},{"id":182,"text":"that takes . \"","depth":12},{"id":183,"text":"In addition to the policy points","depth":8},{"id":184,"text":"that Sanders is expected to push before the convention","depth":8},{"id":185,"text":"- a $ 15 federal minimum wage and a nationwide ban on fracking , for example -","depth":7},{"id":186,"text":"he is also eyeing fundamental reforms to the Democratic nominating process ,","depth":7},{"id":187,"text":"which would have to be made separately from the convention .","depth":7},{"id":188,"text":"The Clinton camp has been extremely careful","depth":7},{"id":189,"text":"not to be seen as urging Sanders to get out of the race ,","depth":8},{"id":190,"text":"keeping in mind her own 2008 campaign against then-Sen. Barack Obama ,","depth":9},{"id":191,"text":"which went until the very end .","depth":9},{"id":192,"text":"Asked whether Sanders should drop out next week","depth":8},{"id":193,"text":"while campaigning in New Jersey last Wednesday ,","depth":8},{"id":194,"text":"former President Bill Clinton declined to weigh in .","depth":8},{"id":195,"text":"\" We should finish the course .","depth":10},{"id":196,"text":"Finish the election , \"","depth":10},{"id":197,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":198,"text":"Nonetheless , some of Sanders ' high-profile backers have been quietly nudging him toward the exit in the name of party unity ,","depth":7},{"id":199,"text":"starting with Oregon Sen. Jeff Merkley , his only Senate endorser ,","depth":8},{"id":200,"text":"who said in April","depth":9},{"id":201,"text":"that he should drop out","depth":10},{"id":202,"text":"if he ' s still trailing Clinton","depth":11},{"id":203,"text":"after the primaries end .","depth":11},{"id":204,"text":"And","depth":9},{"id":205,"text":"as party leaders start openly fretting about uniting the party against Trump ,","depth":10},{"id":206,"text":"the drumbeat has picked up :","depth":10},{"id":207,"text":"\" Sometimes you just have to give up , \"","depth":10},{"id":208,"text":"Senate Minority Leader Harry Reid told The Associated Press on Wednesday .","depth":10},{"id":209,"text":"\" I ' ve never been too good at math ,","depth":11},{"id":210,"text":"but I can figure that one out ,","depth":11},{"id":211,"text":"I think","depth":11},{"id":212,"text":"he better do a little mathing . \"","depth":11},{"id":213,"text":"Even Sanders ' backers are reluctant to publicly offer advice at this point .","depth":11},{"id":214,"text":"Not one of the eight House members","depth":13},{"id":215,"text":"endorsing Sanders","depth":13},{"id":216,"text":"agreed to speak with on record about what he should do .","depth":12},{"id":217,"text":"Yet some vague outlines of Sanders ' coming month-and-a-half are already coming into view , with or without his say .","depth":10},{"id":218,"text":"Some of his highest-profile backers","depth":12},{"id":219,"text":"- including the nurses union , 350.org , the Democratic Socialists of America and the Working Families Party -","depth":12},{"id":220,"text":"are convening a June 17-19 meeting in Chicago","depth":12},{"id":221,"text":"\" to , in part , continue the momentum and movement building","depth":13},{"id":222,"text":"associated with the ongoing Bernie Sanders campaign . ''","depth":13},{"id":223,"text":"The event ,","depth":12},{"id":224,"text":"which is set to include workshops on civil disobedience and building movements ,","depth":12},{"id":225,"text":"is slated to focus on a slate of issues","depth":12},{"id":226,"text":"his campaign team wants to pursue for the convention platform , like the minimum wage hike and a Wall Street speculation tax .","depth":12},{"id":227,"text":"Sanders himself has been invited to join the roster of speakers","depth":10},{"id":228,"text":"that includes a who ' s who of his most prominent surrogates","depth":11},{"id":229,"text":"including Cornel West , Hawaii Rep. Tulsi Gabbard , Arizona Rep. Raúl Grijalva and DeMoro .","depth":11},{"id":230,"text":"\" His candidacy and his potential presidency is about a movement , \"","depth":11},{"id":231,"text":"said DeMoro of Sanders .","depth":11},{"id":232,"text":"\" We had a similar movement , though not of the same magnitude , behind Obama .","depth":11},{"id":233,"text":"But","depth":12},{"id":234,"text":"as soon as he entered office ,","depth":13},{"id":235,"text":"the movement went away . \"","depth":13}],"relations":[{"parent":471,"left":242,"right":470,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":242,"left":240,"right":241,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":240,"left":237,"right":239,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":237,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":239,"left":238,"right":4,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":238,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":241,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":470,"left":314,"right":469,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":314,"left":7,"right":313,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":313,"left":277,"right":312,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":277,"left":243,"right":276,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":243,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":276,"left":248,"right":275,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":248,"left":246,"right":247,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":246,"left":10,"right":245,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":245,"left":244,"right":13,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":244,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":247,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":275,"left":252,"right":274,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":252,"left":249,"right":251,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":249,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":251,"left":18,"right":250,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":250,"left":19,"right":20,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":274,"left":257,"right":273,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":257,"left":254,"right":256,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":254,"left":253,"right":23,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":253,"left":21,"right":22,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":256,"left":24,"right":255,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":255,"left":25,"right":26,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":273,"left":261,"right":272,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":261,"left":259,"right":260,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":259,"left":258,"right":29,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":258,"left":27,"right":28,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":260,"left":30,"right":31,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":272,"left":266,"right":271,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":266,"left":263,"right":265,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":263,"left":262,"right":34,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":262,"left":32,"right":33,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":265,"left":264,"right":37,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":264,"left":35,"right":36,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":271,"left":38,"right":270,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":270,"left":39,"right":269,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":269,"left":40,"right":268,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":268,"left":267,"right":43,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":267,"left":41,"right":42,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":312,"left":280,"right":311,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":280,"left":278,"right":279,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":278,"left":44,"right":45,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":279,"left":46,"right":47,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":311,"left":285,"right":310,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":285,"left":283,"right":284,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":283,"left":48,"right":282,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":282,"left":281,"right":51,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":281,"left":49,"right":50,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":284,"left":52,"right":53,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":310,"left":292,"right":309,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":292,"left":291,"right":61,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":291,"left":288,"right":290,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":288,"left":54,"right":287,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":287,"left":286,"right":57,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":286,"left":55,"right":56,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":290,"left":58,"right":289,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":289,"left":59,"right":60,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":309,"left":308,"right":79,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":308,"left":304,"right":307,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":304,"left":301,"right":303,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":301,"left":293,"right":300,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":293,"left":62,"right":63,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":300,"left":297,"right":299,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":297,"left":294,"right":296,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":294,"left":64,"right":65,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":296,"left":66,"right":295,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":295,"left":67,"right":68,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":299,"left":69,"right":298,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":298,"left":70,"right":71,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":303,"left":72,"right